                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/403" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0062</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10248 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">让“红透”品牌红透中国——中国第一龙虾品牌的成长与烦恼</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Popularize the “Hong Tou” Crayfish Around China ---- The Growth and Pains of The Best Crayfish Brand</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">史有春，李娜等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京星湖饭店</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">市场营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">星湖饭店；刘振海；龙虾；红透品牌；品牌建设；2011百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xinghu Restaurant; Liu Zhenhai; Crayfish; Hong Tou; Brand buildin</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例描述了南京星湖饭店在其总经理刘振海的领导下，如何在濒临倒闭的困境下选择龙虾作为重点菜品进入中高端市场、创建出著名红透龙虾品牌、走出一条低星级宾馆凤凰涅槃之路的全部历程，同时也提出了星湖饭店面临的各种机会和挑战。一个优秀菜品往往能搞活一个饭店，因此本案例描述的情况在餐饮业具有一定的普遍性。然而，为一个菜品注册商标、致力于品牌建设、参与制定行业标准、开展工业化经营、通过品牌加盟拓展外地市场，培育独特的龙虾饮食文化等等，这在餐饮业却很少见，因此本案例所描述的这些事例又是非常具有典型性的。本案例主体虽是饭店，但案例所涉及的产品—市场选择、以及企业领导如何尽心尽力去锻造一个名牌、不断创造辉煌的事例和精神，应该能给其他企业许多启发。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the whole course of “rebirth” for Nanjing Xinghu Restaurant, which under the direction of General-manager Liu Zhenhai, chose crayfish as its specialty, brought crayfish into the middle-end and high-end markets and built the well-known brand “Hong Tou Crayfish”, therefore turned from a low-end hotel to a prosperous restaurant. The case also mentions the various opportunities and challenges faced by Xinghu. An outstanding dish can vitalize a restaurant, so the case may be universally applied in catering industry. However, it is also rare for a restaurant to register trademark for one dish, to make efforts in building brand, establishing industry standards, applying industrialized operation, developing outer markets through franchise, and cultivating unique crayfish culture. Therefore this case is quite unique in catering industry on the other hand. We hope that the description of how the entrepreneurs made product-market selections, how they kept building a brand, can bring some inspiration to other enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌与行业或品类的兴旺、竞争优势、品牌营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010-11</td>
                            </tr>
